      "title": "The import of over 300 items is suspended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Finance has decided to temporarily suspend the import of more than 300 products including milk powder, yogurt, fruits, chocolate, perfumes, cosmetics, clothes, air conditioners, refrigerators, household electrical appliances, telephones."
